{"type": "article", "id": 25364, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-13T07:14:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26163, "name": "视觉设计"}, {"id": 3255, "name": "Menu"}, {"id": 26164, "name": "Northern Lighting"}, {"id": 26165, "name": "Afteroom"}, {"id": 26166, "name": "Sander Lorier"}, {"id": 26167, "name": "Juno Jeon"}, {"id": 26168, "name": "Scott Pancioli"}, {"id": 26169, "name": "Adamantia Chatzivasileiou"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071048493ewUjqINfsx9yYd2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Family benches by Afteroom &amp; Menu </h2>\n<p>这张长椅带有小型的圆边桌，是瑞典设计团队 Afteroom 为丹麦家居品牌 Menu 设计的。椭圆形的座位面采用了皮革，结构是很细的金属管，在中间的位置连接了大理石的圆桌面，两者之间也构成了一种对比和平衡，很典雅。他们曾经发布了一个带有三只腿的椅子与此类似，可以适合家庭或餐厅等多个场合。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337075qPWDQNTBf8ln1rG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133707DZvdYEtSLjzXIUeO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23931624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133708BnbRwiXL31F7aGyd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68269231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133708HwPg3SWy1xQlbTjL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80128205\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133709GyLVqfaiUnhmDQ7p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Drift by Nestor Campos &amp; Northern Lighting</h2>\n<p>这个黑色的方形“纸片”是一个烛台，是用金属做的。一个角离开桌面微微折起来以方便移动，它构成了微妙的深浅阴影对比，在视觉上给人一种轻盈的感受。一套 4 个烛台可以拼在一起或分开，构成有变化的图案。烛台中间有钉子插上蜡烛，可以适合不同型号。设计师来自西班牙，是为挪威品牌 Northern Lighting 而设计，<a href=\"https://northernlighting.no/news/drift-a-union-of-fire-and-ice/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133709UWyQvZ518LfjnBH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133710ZBNH84FAOprd7G1a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337109IzhSvpO4QZKowqX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133711hkKAgCfVv8LBH31s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Branch-out by Sander Lorier</h2>\n<p>这个像树枝一样的结构串起了桌子、灯和盆景，但树枝的关节处是可以拆装或旋转的，意味着这三者之间的关系更加灵活，可以是一个长枝干带有灯和盆景，也可以是边桌上长出一盏灯。枝干结构本身模拟了自然的状态，这个设计也想给居住环境更多的变化。设计师 Sander Lorier 来自荷兰，售价 599 欧元，<a href=\"http://studiolorier.com/product/branch-out/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337112rTbo0J1cg5zHwt3.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7475\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337126lz4SEoLhGP7gs5C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133713i6ZK5D1h7RgAro9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133713DFcemGap2x4HS3Jj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337147sjrZEo4ItYgXWmK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“pull me to live”by Juno Jeon</h2>\n<p>这两件家具都能随着开合与人互动。抽屉的表面覆盖了一些小的“鳞片”，拉开抽屉的过程也拨动了“鳞片”本身，可以看到它像波浪一样滑动的效果。另一个柜子的柜门则会随着人的走动变换颜色，两种设计都带给空间更多的趣味。设计师 Juno Jeon 是在荷兰学习的韩国人，<a href=\"http://www.junojunos.com\">这里是他的主页。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133714RNrvdDTc8K0j4gUk.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133715lfXvwn3IZgSV1ihx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133716T3jX6MwHSIDdyLpW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133716Pc1F0plTtsOfgzMY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133717rHoNF3sjnS1YuUPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Electrolux Verse by Scott Pancioli</h2>\n<p>这款吸尘器的概念设计来自美国设计师 Scott Pancioli，吸头是一个圆环，相当于使用一次有两次的效果。圆环吸头和手柄的倾斜角度经过了调整，当手拿着吸尘器时，不会因为用力下压而断裂。流线的外形黑白色搭配让这款吸尘器设计很简洁，也能更加融入现代家居生活的环境中。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337182nuYofl46OayMPTE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133718h4eMKgOCRa0j5ZyX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133719wzRu2p07JnrI1daF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133719CT3AqbGrU7zS5DYl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337206nZNbldaTHMW2DJE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>The Voodootricks album cover by Adamantia Chatzivasileiou</h2>\n<p>这盘专辑是为一个名叫 The Voodootricks 的音乐团队设计的，他们擅长 rap，音乐灵感来自希腊当地的文化。专辑的封面则强调了这种联系，最外一层的黑色盒子带有镂空的乐队的名字，而下面蓝色的图像是雅典城，重叠在一起时可以隐约看到建筑的背景。黑色的专辑色调搭配亮丽的蓝色可以展示出独特和这种异域风格。设计师是来自希腊的 90 后，<a href=\"http://www.adamantiachatzivasileiou.com/Work-1/The-Voodootricks-Album-cover\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133720Wd2t3zyg07AnJVhx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133721K5atAV07mHBbd61S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133721h8NglRwtsfKMcyzY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133722YyOpCJxP6VnLN3c5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337222LrS84e5sacbjKAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}